{
  "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "我们熟悉的整数排在一条数轴上，但如果把它们搬进复平面呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 44064,
      "text": "高斯把整数推广成 a 加 b 乘 i 的形式，其中 a、b 都是普通整数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "于是无数个点整齐地铺满复平面，排成一张方格点阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "norm",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "norm-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/norm-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "每个高斯整数都有一个范数，等于 a 的平方加 b 的平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "norm",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "norm-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/norm-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "它正好是这个点到原点距离的平方，把复数的大小变回了整数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "norm",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "norm-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/norm-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "范数是乘法的好帮手：两数相乘，范数也相乘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "prime",
      "line_id": "gp-1",
      "filename": "prime-gp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/prime-gp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "有些高斯整数无法再拆成更小的因子，它们就是高斯素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "prime",
      "line_id": "gp-2",
      "filename": "prime-gp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/prime-gp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.59,
      "size": 41472,
      "text": "若点落在坐标轴上，只有绝对值是 4k+3 型素数的才算高斯素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "prime",
      "line_id": "gp-3",
      "filename": "prime-gp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/prime-gp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "若点不在轴上，则当它的范数是普通素数时，它就是高斯素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "split",
      "line_id": "sp-1",
      "filename": "split-sp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/split-sp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "把普通素数放进高斯整数，会发生奇妙的变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "split",
      "line_id": "sp-2",
      "filename": "split-sp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/split-sp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "像 5、13 这样 4k+1 型的素数会分裂成一对共轭高斯素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "split",
      "line_id": "sp-3",
      "filename": "split-sp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/split-sp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "而 3、7 这样 4k+3 型的素数依然坚守素性，2 则发生分歧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "缩放显示范围，看高斯素数在复平面上铺开的花瓣图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "你会发现它关于两条轴、还关于对角线，呈现完美的八重对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "高斯整数把整数搬上复平面，范数衡量它们的大小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gaussian-integers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "高斯素数按简单规则判定，分布对称而优美。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gaussian-integers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
